<li>Filmfare Award - Telugu Film Industry	Best Actress Fidaa (2017)</li>

<li>Special Award	Best Female Debut Premam (2015)</li>

<li>IBNLive Movie Awards 2016 for Best Southern Debut Premam (2015)</li>

<li>SIIMA - Telugu	Best Actress Fidaa (2017)</li>

<li>SIIMA - Malayalam Best Debut Actress Premam (2015)</li>

<li>Vanitha Film Award Best Debut Actress Premam (2015)</li>
</ul>

